channel.title: 562/668 Editing the Cache
channel.description:
Hi,
I wanted to edit the cache of my 668 cache. I found several cache editors but they all have had errors reading them. Is there anyone who has a 667+ cache editor which works and is easy to use? All i want to do is change the background and logo.
Thank You.
